@page "/headings"
<PageTitle>Headings (H1–H6) - Saascade Docs</PageTitle>

<h1>Headings (H1–H6)</h1>

<main class="documentation">

    <section class="card">

        <h2>Overview</h2>

        <p class="subtitle">
            The <code>&lt;H1&gt;</code> through <code>&lt;H6&gt;</code> components
            render semantic heading elements with design-system-aware styling.
        </p>

        <hr />

        <h3>Basic Usage</h3>

        <pre><code>&lt;H1&gt;Main Title&lt;/H1&gt;
&lt;H2&gt;Section Title&lt;/H2&gt;
&lt;H3&gt;Subsection Title&lt;/H3&gt;
&lt;H4&gt;Sub-subsection&lt;/H4&gt;
&lt;H5&gt;Minor Heading&lt;/H5&gt;
&lt;H6&gt;Smallest Heading&lt;/H6&gt;</code></pre>

    </section>

    <section class="card">

        <h2>Visual Hierarchy</h2>

        <p>Each heading level decreases in size and visual weight:</p>

        <div style="padding: 16px 0;">
            <h1 style="margin: 8px 0;">H1 — Main Title</h1>
            <h2 style="margin: 8px 0;">H2 — Section Title</h2>
            <h3 style="margin: 8px 0;">H3 — Subsection</h3>
            <h4 style="margin: 8px 0;">H4 — Sub-subsection</h4>
        </div>

    </section>

    <section class="card">

        <h2>Parameters</h2>

        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Type</th><th>Description</th></tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr><td>Class</td><td>string?</td><td>Additional CSS classes.</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Style</td><td>string?</td><td>Inline styles.</td></tr>
                <tr><td>ChildContent</td><td>RenderFragment</td><td>Heading text.</td></tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>

    </section>

</main>
